entry.name: OR Pilot - MBARI OR Algae
entry.description: Proteins from marine microbial community were extracted, trypsine digested and identified with LC-MS/MS analysis.

additional_fields.field: SDS boiling-based protein extraction and FASP-based protein cleanup and digestion.
Searches were performed with Sipros and filtered with 1% FDR at the peptide level and two peptides per protein.
No PTMs are included in the dataset
